Linear layout
Linear layout  are sued when we want to arrange the widgets in a linear manner on the screen

Relative layout
Relative layouts are used when we want to arrange the widgets in relation to one other or in relation
to the screen

Conventions for writing the id's

TextView - txt<purpose>
ImageView - img<purpose>
Button - btn<purpose>
EditText - et<purpose>

TextSize is not applicable in edit text option